title: Ep 23 - Overcoming Rejection
itunes:title: Ep 23 - Overcoming Rejection
description:
Rejection can be tough. It can feel like a setback and sometimes even paralyze us, but in order to be successful we must realize that rejection is part of success. On the road to living the life of our dreams we will be rejected over and over again, so we must become okay with rejection and not let it hold us back. In this episode give tips on how to overcome rejection and how to psychologically set ourselves up to embrace rejection.
